  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether insulin resistance might affect the
      pathogenesis of hypertensive disorders in pregnancy since midtrimester. Furthermore, markers
      of vascular and placental injuries, of oxidative stress and inflammation will be evaluated.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
