    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  PCOS, BMI&gt;/=30

          -  previous pregnancy affected by hypertension or gestational diabetes

          -  thrombophilia

          -  Type I or II diabetes mellitus

          -  autoimmune diseases

          -  twin pregnancy

          -  renal diseases

          -  previous pre-eclampsia in relatives
